oslevel - Know the OS Version
prtconf - hardware information
lscfg | grep proc - CPU monitoring
topas - provide the overview of the system
iostat  - Monitor the devices / I/O statics/monitoring
lvmstat - To monitor LVM
SAR - System activity report
lparstat - lpar statics
vmstat - display virtual memory statics/paging space.
ifconfig - Network adaptor configre information
bootinfo -r - get physical memort information
Netstat- Network monitor


CPU Monitoring -	vmstat, iostat, topas, sar, time/timex
Memory Monitoring -	vmstat, topas, ps, lsps, ipcs
I/O Subsystem -	vmstat, topas, iostat, lvmstat, lsps, lsatt/lsdev, lspv/lsvg/lslv
Network	- netstat, topas, atmstat, entstat, tokstat, fddistat, nfsstat, ifconfig
Processes & Threads -	ps, pstat, topas
schedo -L - process scheduler
nmon - Network monitoring




